<h2 id="편미분">편미분</h2>

<h2 id="chain-rule">Chain Rule</h2>

<p>인라인 수식: \(\sum_{i=0}^n i^2 = \frac{n(n+1)(2n+1)}{6}\)</p>

\[\frac{\partial f\left(x,y\right)}{\partial x}\ =\ \frac{\partial \left(2x\ +\ 3xy\ +{y}^3\right)}{\partial x}\ =\ 2\ +\ 3y\]
